    "On macOS 14 Sonoma and Later, Location Services permission is required to get Wi-Fi SSIDs.\nPlease enable Location Services in System Preferences > Security & Privacy > Privacy > Location Services." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在 macOS 14 Sonoma 及更新版本中，需要使用定位服务权限才能获取 Wi-Fi SSID。\n请在「系统设置」>「隐私与安全性」>「定位服务」中启用。"
